<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="74" >Kakakikiri@Veeさんは No.535「Re:IKS/SHD武器強(3)のLOG」で書きました。
>SHD Guildの武器アップグレード(3)クエストのLogです。
>
>You say, 'hail Lord Korzin'
>
>Lord Korzin says 'What is it you seek?  Eternal suffering? 
>
>You say, 'what is a eternal suffering'
>
>Lord Korzin says 'Then follow the words of Cazic-Thule and may his 
>blessed curses rain upon your soul as they shall on all of his faithful 
>servants. 
>
>You say, 'what is a skull of torture?'
>
>Lord Korzin says 'You were sent to me.  You must be the squire who 
>found the ancient tome, 'The Origins of Pain'.  I can use a talented 
>crusader such as yourself.  In my dreams, Cazic-Thule has spoken to me. 
> He instructed me to seek out the 'Skull of Torture' which was last 
>reported to be within the torture tower of the ancient Lord of Pain, 
>Kurn.  Will you [accept the calling]?. 
>
>You say, 'i will accept the calling'
>
>Lord Korzin says 'As if you had a choice.  Seek out the tower of Kurn 
>and find the Skull of Torture.  You should be able to easily recognize 
>this skull as it glows with the power of Cazic Thule. Return it to me 
>with your squire's khukri and I shall reward you with the knight's 
>khukri.  Go at once. 
>
>A Glowing Skull（かなりレアっぽい感じ）
>と Squire's Khukri を返却します
>
>Lord Korzin says 'You will be rewarded with the knight's khukri when I 
>have possesion of your squire's khukri and the Skull of Torture. 
>
>Lord Korzin says 'Excellent work!  You are no squire.  You are now a 
>knight of the crusaders.  Your next step shall be zealot.  And every 
>zealot wields a magical khukri. 
>
>Your faction standing with CrusadersOfGreenmist got better.
>Your faction standing with LegionOfCabilis got better.
>You receive 8 gold from Lord Korzin.
>
>で、
>Knight's Khukri
>1HS	6/24 INT+3 Magic Lore ND が貰えます。
